revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yeagleys}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yeagley'' is the 25226<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 982 individuals. ''Yeagley'' is most common among White (93.69%) individuals.
